cc:Work.dc:title: Electric Components Library
cc:Work.dc:description: A library of SVG symbols to be used in electric and electronic circuit diagrams in Wikimedia Projects.

text.tspan: - Wire corners and ends are sharp, not rounded.
- Font: Times New Roman (6 pt) or Linux Libertine (6 pt)
- Component reference designators are italicized, and (symbols of) physical quantities use a regular font style.
- All wire nodes are grid-aligned. In Inkscape, press # to see the grid.
Open Source Electrical Symbol Library - V1.0
